# first degree polynomial

.EQ
P(x) = ax + a sub 0
.EN

the secret_key is given by: a sub 0

a sub 0 is known when we have two points
each point is independently saved


# n degree polynomial

.EQ
P(x) = a sub n x sup n +
a sub {n−1} x sup {n−1} +
a sub {n−2} x sup {n−2} +
.... +
a sub 0
.EN

the secret key is given by: a sub 0

a sub 0 is known when we have n points
each point is independently saved


